' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  SERVICE DEPENDENCIES  (uses / calls)
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
AppInitializer ..> OCRService               : initializes
AppInitializer ..> EmotionDetectionService  : initializes
AppInitializer ..> DepthEstimationService   : initializes
AppInitializer ..> OfflineModeService       : pings server
AppInitializer ..> LocationService          : requestPermissions
AppInitializer ..> ObjectDetectionService   : loadModel / requestPermissions
AppInitializer ..> SpatialAudioService      : initializes
AppInitializer ..> BluetoothService         : initializes
AppInitializer ..> NavigationService        : stopNavigation (cleanup)
AppInitializer ..> ARService                : dispose (cleanup)
AppInitializer ..> TextToSpeechService      : speaks status

ObjectDetectionService ..> HazardScoringService : scoreDetection

FootPlacementService ..> TextToSpeechService    : speak
FootPlacementService ..> SpatialAudioService    : playDirectionalBeep

NavigationService ..> LocationService           : getCurrentLocation / watch
NavigationService ..> TextToSpeechService       : speak
NavigationService ..> SpatialAudioService       : playNavigationCue

GoogleMapsService ..> TextToSpeechService       : speak
GoogleMapsService ..> SpatialAudioService       : playDirectionalBeep

EmergencyService ..> TextToSpeechService        : speak
EmergencyService ..> LocationService            : getCurrentLocation

WearablesService ..> BluetoothService           : delegate
WearablesService ..> TextToSpeechService        : speak

VoiceCommandService ..> TextToSpeechService     : speak
VoiceCommandService ..> ObjectDetectionService  : context
VoiceCommandService ..> LocationService         : getCurrentLocation
VoiceCommandService ..> MicToneService          : playOn / playOff
VoiceCommandService ..> EmergencyService        : dynamic require

RouteMemoryService ..> LocationService          : calculateDistance
RouteMemoryService ..> TextToSpeechService      : speak

OCRService ..> OfflineModeService               : imported
EmotionDetectionService ..> TextToSpeechService : speak

